span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">会议以投票表决方式审议通过了《关于罗熹、李福利职务任免的议案》。罗熹不再担任公司总经理职务，聘任李福利为公司副总经理。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">表决结果：同意<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">6</span>票、反对<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">0</span>票、弃权<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">0</span>票。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">华润集团董事会</span><br style=\"overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\" />\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">二○一八年九月二十日</span></p>\r\n<body id=\"cke_pastebin\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 200px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden; left: -1000px;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: -webkit-right; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: -webkit-right; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">华润集团董事会</span><br style=\"overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\" />\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: -webkit-right; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">二○一八年九月二十日</span></body>\r\n', '0', '', '0', '10000', 'show', '0', '', '0', '1', '集团办公厅|0'), ('16', '<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 15px;\">为全面回顾改革开放</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">40</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 15px;\">年来波澜壮阔的伟大历程，生动展现中央企业改革开放以来特别是十八大以来取得的辉煌成就，国资委宣传局决定在中央企业开展&ldquo;走进新时代展现新形象&mdash;中国石化长城润滑油杯纪念改革开放</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">40</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 15px;\">周年中央企业故事大赛&rdquo;。为响应国资委号召，积极参与活动，展现华润所属企业和员工的风采，集团现以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">SBU/BU</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 15px;\">为单位，面向全体员工征稿，请各位文学爱好者踊跃参加。现将有关事项通知如下：</span>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">一、<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">&nbsp;</span>活动主题</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">活动以&ldquo;走进新时代展现新形象&rdquo;为主题，围绕改革开放的伟大意义、历史成就、成功实践、经验启示、重点人物等方面内容，讲述企业故事，展现改革开放<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">40</span>年来特别是十八大以来，华润所属企业取得的历史性成就，发生的历史性变革，达到展示形象、凝聚力量、弘扬精神、塑造品牌的良好效果。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">二、<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">&nbsp;</span>征集内容</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">请集团文学爱好者充分发挥积极性与创造性，立足单位实际，深入挖掘，围绕以下主题内容进行创作：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">（一）&nbsp;围绕国有资本保值增值、国有经济壮大、国家战略实施与重点项目建设等内容，创作企业重大改革发展成就类故事。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">（二）&nbsp;围绕国企国资改革、科技创新、治理模式优化、发展转型升级等内容，创作企业改革实践类故事。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">（三）&nbsp;围绕实施国际化经营、践行&ldquo;一带一路&rdquo;倡议等内容，创作企业开放发展类故事。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">（四）&nbsp;围绕培育国企精神与企业家精神，弘扬工匠精神、劳模精神等内容，创作企业文化品牌故事与先进人物类故事。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">三、&nbsp;相关要求</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">上报故事应为文字类作品，要求主题明确、文字生动，具有较强的可读性、思想性和故事性。每个故事篇幅控制在<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">3000</span>字以内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">四、<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">&nbsp;</span>推进阶段</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">集团办公厅将对各单位报送内容择优筛选<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">10</span>&mdash;&mdash;<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">20</span>篇，上报至国资委宣传局，参加全国央企故事评选。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">（一）&nbsp;故事征集阶段（即日起&mdash;&mdash;<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">2018</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">10</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">10</span>日截稿）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">（二）&nbsp;后续选评阶段（<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">2018</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">10</span>月下旬&mdash;&mdash;<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">11</span>月）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">（三）宣传发布阶段（<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">2018</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">I2</span>月上中旬）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">活动主办单位拟定于<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">12</span>月上旬，与主流媒体合作，各中央企业也将釆取多种形式，充分利用网站、报纸、微信等自有媒体进行联动宣传；国资委宣传局将充分利用国资委网站、国资小新、国企开放日、&ldquo;国企文化&rdquo;微信公众账号等平台，同步展现精品故事。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">五、&nbsp;报送方式</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">各单位将组织开展征稿活动，以<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">SBU/BU</span>为单位统一征集、筛选，择优推荐，报送至集团办公厅企业文化处。所有单位投稿于<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">10&nbsp;</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: visible !important; word-break: normal !important;\">10</span>日前截稿。请各位作者注意本单位征稿通知，积极参与。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0px 16px